## Critical Layout & Styling Rules

### Video Container Hierarchy (MUST MAINTAIN)
\`\`\`tsx
// video-editor.tsx - Wrapper with flex space
<div className="flex flex-1 flex-col min-h-0 overflow-hidden">
  <div className="flex-1 min-h-0">
    <VideoPreview ... />
  </div>
</div>

// video-preview.tsx - Container with explicit dimensions
<div className="relative flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-black">
  <video className="w-full h-full object-contain" />
</div>
\`\`\`

**Why this matters:**
- `min-h-0` prevents flex items from refusing to shrink
- `h-full w-full` ensures proper filling
- `object-contain` maintains aspect ratio
- `overflow-hidden` prevents layout breaks

### Known Issue & Solution
**Issue**: Video only displays in fullscreen, black screen in normal view
**Solution**: Proper flex hierarchy with `min-h-0` and wrapper div with `flex-1`

