## Testing Scenarios
Must pass:
- [ ] Record 30-second screen capture → timeline
- [x] Import 3 clips and arrange in sequence
- [x] Trim and split clips
- [ ] Export 2-minute video with multiple clips
- [ ] Screen + webcam overlay
- [ ] Test on macOS (primary) and Windows if possible

## Performance Targets
- Timeline responsive with 10+ clips ✅
- Preview at 30 fps minimum ✅
- Export completes without crashes ⏳
- App launch under 5 seconds ⏳
- No memory leaks (15+ minute test) ⏳

## Submission Requirements (Wednesday 10:59 PM CT)
